text: The Originals is an American supernatural show. It's began airing on The CW in October 2013. On May 2017 the series was renewed for a fifth and final season which aired from April to August 2017. ==Cast== *Joseph Morgan as Klaus Mikaelson *Daniel Gillies as Elijah Mikaelson *Phoebe Tonkin as Hayley Marshall *Daniella Campbell as Davina Claire *Claire Holt as Rebekah Mikaelson *Charles Mikael Davis as Marcel Gerard *Leah Pipes as Camille ==Reception== The show has received generally high reviews from critics such as Rotten Tomatoes. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:American television series Category:2013 American television series debuts
